== 使用方式 ==
{{Lua|Module:Math}}

This template performs addition. For example, if you want to add 2 and 3, use this: <nowiki>{{Sum|2|3}}</nowiki>, which creates {{Sum|2|3}}. It handles positive and negative integers, decimals, and fractions to thirteen decimal points:
*<nowiki>{{sum|-3|1}}</nowiki> produces: {{sum|-3|1}}
*<nowiki>{{sum|1|0.5}}</nowiki> produces: {{sum|1|0.5}}
*<nowiki>{{sum|1|2/3}}</nowiki> produces: {{sum|1|2/3}}
It also handles some symbols such as "pi" ({{pi}}):
*<nowiki>{{sum|pi|0}}</nowiki> produces {{sum|pi|0}}
More than two parameters may be employed:
*<nowiki>{{sum|1|1|1}}</nowiki> produces {{sum|1|1|1}}

